work.ca/article/kitchenaid-go-cordless-hand-blender-honest-review/\"\u003eOur Honest Review of the New KitchenAid Go Cordless Hand Blender\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eWe ordered the bundle shortly after the holidays to test how well the set works with a variety of foods and drinks. Included in the set is cold smoke wood chip sample flavours (hickory and applewood) that we also used in testing. You can also buy \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.ca/Breville-BSM600AWC-Smoking-Wood-Chips/dp/B07168H4SG?crid=ACJ3JEDJUJGQ\u0026amp;keywords=breville+smoking+gun+wood+chips\u0026amp;qid=1707240313\u0026amp;sprefix=breville+smoking%2Caps%2C96\u0026amp;sr=8-2\u0026amp;linkCode=ll1\u0026amp;tag=foodnetworkca-20\u0026amp;linkId=b318ac079a34fccb5a5f890a84fda248\u0026amp;language=en_CA\u0026amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eBreville\u0026rsquo;s woodchip bundle in additional flavours\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e like cherrywood and mesquite or \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.ca/Natural-Chips%EF%BC%8CSmoking-Fashioned-Cocktails%EF%BC%8C-Cocktails%EF%BC%8CDrinks%EF%BC%8CCheese%EF%BC%8CFood/dp/B09R3KVQP4?crid=ACJ3JEDJUJGQ\u0026amp;keywords=breville+smoking+gun+wood+chips\u0026amp;qid=1707240389\u0026amp;sprefix=breville+smoking%2Caps%2C96\u0026amp;sr=8-1-spons\u0026amp;sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9hdGY\u0026amp;psc=1\u0026amp;linkCode=ll1\u0026amp;tag=foodnetworkca-20\u0026amp;linkId=c2f9e3c6c9ba0219e2fbc2026b27495f\u0026amp;language=en_CA\u0026amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eother brands\u0026rsquo; versions too\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e.\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_149703\" style=\"width: 858px\" class=\